Package: abettor
Title: R bindings to Betfair API-NG
Version: 0.1.5
Date: 2015-11-11
Authors@R: as.person(c("Phill Clarke <phill@starkingdom.co.uk> [aut, cre]",
                       "David Sheehan <davidfsheehan87@gmail.com> [aut]",
                       "Alvise Trevian <a.trevisan@enpicom.com> [ctb]"))
Description: An R package for connecting to the online betting exchange,
    Betfair, via their API-NG product using JSON-RPC. The package user can
    retrieve market information and place bets.
Depends:
    R (>= 3.1.1)
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://github.com/tobiasstrebitzer/abettor
BugReports: http://www.github.com/tobiasstrebitzer/abettor/issues
Maintainer: Phill Clarke <phill@starkingdom.co.uk>
LazyData: true
Imports:
    httr (>= 1.4.0),
    RCurl (>= 1.95-4.3),
    jsonlite (>= 0.9.12)
Suggests:
    knitr,
    rmarkdown
VignetteBuilder: knitr
RoxygenNote: 5.0.1
